text: The Port of Pasni () is located in Pasni City in the Balochistan province of Pakistan. The facilities include modern fish harbour, port, and a naval base for the Pakistan Navy.Pakistan Naval Bases ==See also== *Pasni Fish Harbour ==References== Category:Populated places in Balochistan, Pakistan Category:Ports and harbours of Pakistan Category:Coastal cities and towns in Pakistan
title: Port of Pasni
